    {
      "id": "el_14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 481,
      "width": 398,
      "height": 281,
      "text": "Pure recurring (0.xxx...):\n  0.ababab... = ab / 99\n  0.abcabc... = abc / 999\n  Denominator = as many 9s as repeating digits\n\nMixed recurring (0.x_yyy...):\n  0.1666... = (16-1)/90 = 15/90 = 1/6\n  Formula: (entire - non-repeating) /\n           (9s for repeating, 0s for non-repeating)\n\n  0.16̄ = (16-1)/90 = 1/6\n  0.123̄ = (123-12)/900 = 111/900 = 37/300\n\nWHY: x=0.abab..., 100x=ab.abab...\n  100x-x=ab → 99x=ab → x=ab/99\n\nEx: 0.272727... → 27/99 = 3/11\n  Verify: 3÷11 = 0.272727... ✓",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 14,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Pure recurring (0.xxx...):\n  0.ababab... = ab / 99\n  0.abcabc... = abc / 999\n  Denominator = as many 9s as repeating digits\n\nMixed recurring (0.x_yyy...):\n  0.1666... = (16-1)/90 = 15/90 = 1/6\n  Formula: (entire - non-repeating) /\n           (9s for repeating, 0s for non-repeating)\n\n  0.16̄ = (16-1)/90 = 1/6\n  0.123̄ = (123-12)/900 = 111/900 = 37/300\n\nWHY: x=0.abab..., 100x=ab.abab...\n  100x-x=ab → 99x=ab → x=ab/99\n\nEx: 0.272727... → 27/99 = 3/11\n  Verify: 3÷11 = 0.272727... ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
