    {
      "id": "el_20",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 922,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 23÷5=4 rem 3 → 23/5=4 3/5\nStep 2: 4 3/7=(4×7+3)/7=31/7\n  Verify: 31÷7=4 rem 3=4 3/7 ✓\n\nTRICK (quick rules):\nImproper→Mixed: divide, quotient=whole\n  remainder stays as numerator\nMixed→Improper: (whole×den+num)/den\n\n  23/5:  5 ) 23\n           20   (5×4)\n           ──\n            3   rem → 4 3/5\n\n  4 3/7: (4×7+3)/7 = 31/7\n\nAnswer: 23/5 = 4 3/5 and 4 3/7 = 31/7 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
