    {
      "id": "el_40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1332,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 3/5×10/9 = 30/45 = 2/3\n  4/7÷2/3 = 4/7×3/2 = 12/14 = 6/7\n\nTRICK (cancel before multiply):\n3/5 × 10/9: cancel 3↔9(÷3), 5↔10(÷5)\n= (1×2)/(1×3) = 2/3 (small numbers!)\n\nDivision: flip & multiply\n4/7 ÷ 2/3 → 4/7 × 3/2\nCancel 4↔2: = 2×3/(7×1) = 6/7\n\nTIP: Always cancel BEFORE multiplying\n\nAnswer: 2/3 and 6/7 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 40,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 3/5×10/9 = 30/45 = 2/3\n  4/7÷2/3 = 4/7×3/2 = 12/14 = 6/7\n\nTRICK (cancel before multiply):\n3/5 × 10/9: cancel 3↔9(÷3), 5↔10(÷5)\n= (1×2)/(1×3) = 2/3 (small numbers!)\n\nDivision: flip & multiply\n4/7 ÷ 2/3 → 4/7 × 3/2\nCancel 4↔2: = 2×3/(7×1) = 6/7\n\nTIP: Always cancel BEFORE multiplying\n\nAnswer: 2/3 and 6/7 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
