    {
      "id": "el_60",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1713,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 'of'=multiply\n  Num: 2/3×9/4=18/12=3/2\n  Den: 3/2×4/5=12/10=6/5\nStep 2: (3/2)÷(6/5)=3/2×5/6=15/12=5/4\n\nTRICK (cancel early):\n2/3×9/4: cancel 2↔4, 3↔9 → 1×3/1×2=3/2\n3/2×4/5: cancel 2↔4 → 3×2/1×5=6/5\nThen: 3/2×5/6: cancel 3↔6 → 1×5/2×2=5/4\n\n  ┌───────────────────────┐\n  │  (3/2) ÷ (6/5)       │\n  │  = 3/2 × 5/6 = 5/4   │\n  └───────────────────────┘\n\nAnswer: 5/4 or 1 1/4 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
